data.name: FUR BRAWLS - Dark Bunnies
data.description:
[furbrawls.io](https://www.furbrawls.io/)

[Super Tigers](https://opensea.io/collection/super-tigers)

Super Bunnies are rare generative hand-drawn superheroes sworn to protect our universe. 
Dark Super Bunnies are opposed by their hero counterparts the Light Super Bunnies. The perfect balance for the universe. Yin Yang and the never ending battle between good and evil.

A community-driven project, each bunny is your membership card and gives you a vote in our collective future: the first being how to forge our immersive ecosystem, where a slick multiplayer FPS game is already being explored – one that allows people to fight as their bunny avatars and earn NFTs and tokens as they subdue humanity.

Starting from a limited edition of 5K on the Ethereum chain, their origin story includes a deflationary breeding mechanism (burning Bunnies for even rarer creatures). Every bunny is uniquely made from over 150 different features - no unpopular attributes! 'GOD MODE' anyone?

data.name: Futura 2000
data.description: Artist FUTURA2000—most commonly known as a pioneer in New York’s “Subway School” of Graffiti, and as a forefather of global streetwear—has an almost three-decade career as an early mover in another genre of creativity: Digital Art. Inspired by seminal life events such as his seeing responsive HUD displays on fighter jets while serving in the US Navy, to ingesting the dense compositional architecture and technological overlays of Stanley Kubrick’s "2OO1: A Space Odyssey” in 1968, Futura’s mind has always had a driving undercurrent from “The Grid.” Now, in 2021, the creation, distribution, and transaction of art on a digital platform is simultaneously welcomed—as it is perhaps overdue, unique to him.

data.name: Fvckrender x Victor Mosquera
data.description:
Victor Mosquera drops his second collection!

Victor Mosquera is a Vancouver, B.C. based artist creating works influenced by psychedelia and the ethereal intersection between consciousness and the subliminal. His unique and immediately recognizable style lead him to work on a series of AAA games with Ubisoft including Watchdogs Legion, FarCry 5 & Starlink. In concert with his work in the video game world he has been called upon to lend his artistic vision to a number of musical projects, including working with Willo Perron on the visuals for Kid Cudi’s 2019 Coachella performance, working closely with Grammy-nominated electronic duo Odesza on the identity for their destination festival Sundara and numerous projects for their label/creative agency Foreign Family Collective. He has also worked with The New York Times on the cover of their Rabbit Hole Podcast, Universal Music Group, Interscope Records, Scientific American, GJones and Dirty Heads, among others.

data.name: Fyat Lux (Dawn Collection)
data.description:
FYAT LUX [ fē-ˌät-ˈlu̇ks ] : an epic saga that spans the digital and physical worlds.

Set thousands of years after an event called the Flux stopped all technology from working, rare people called Sparks are born with the ability to turn on ancient technology from humanity's golden age. 

The Fyat Lux Dawn collection consists of 8080 Sparks from the Fyat Lux universe. Each NFT is a metaverse-ready 3D avatar masterpiece, generated from 200 meticulously crafted traits. Each NFT is tethered to a unique "phygital" smart card that allows the holder to view the Spark in AR.

Designed to be beautiful in 2D and 3D, available both physically and digitally, these NFTs transcend dimensions and realities.

data.name: Gachapon.xyz Capsule Series 1
data.description:
Inspired by Gachapon capsule machines, Gacha Gacha ART series 1 is a fun way to collect unique art on the blockchain by amazing established and emerging artists from around the world! You'll be surprised and excited about your new NFT-based art piece, whether it's the one you were hoping for or not. The Gacha Gacha ART community offers a way to trade and sell your pieces to get all of the ones you want. Good luck!

## What is Gacha Gacha ART?

Gacha Gacha ART is a collaborative art project featuring nine artists creating multiple artworks. Inspired by Gachapon machines in Japan that give out random capsule toys, buying a Gacha Gacha ART will get you one random NFT created by one of the artists. There is a chance to get duplicates as well as a chance of getting a one off.

EXCLUSIVE CLAIM FOR BLOOT HOLDERS

data.name: Gavin Shapiro
data.description:
Gavin Shapiro is a digital artist whose ultimate goal is to produce work that makes you smile. He focuses primarily on playful conceptual artworks that explore how we can use digital tools to confront our expectations of what’s possible in a traditionally physical art world. He's lived in New York, Osaka and Paris, working on a large variety of projects including tv shows, commercials, outdoor displays, large-format stage visuals, and animations for casino games. 

His personal work, released under the name “shapiro500,” has been used as visuals at music festivals and concerts all over the world, and has been shown on digital billboards as part of art exhibitions in New York City and Tokyo. His animations have accumulated hundreds of millions of views across Instagram, Facebook, Reddit, and Giphy, and have been sold as NFTs on Nifty Gateway and SuperRare since mid-2020.

data.name: Gems of Awareness by Alex Grey & Allyson Grey
data.description: The Gems of Awareness collection of unique NFT Animations, are crystallizations of our psychedelic visionary experiences. They portray the elevation of consciousness and identity with a higher power, languages of the Spirit and spectral geometries of the Soul. We are both painters, so each animation was based on a specific work and expanded by animation to new dimensions. Gems of Awareness, the first NFTs by artists Alex Grey & Allyson Grey, in collaboration with Trippy are offered to raise funds to complete Entheon, Sanctuary of Visionary Art at CoSM, an art church in the Hudson Valley of New York. This three story, 12,000 square foot art temple, scheduled to open in mid 2022, will exhibit works of the International Visionary Art movement portraying glimpses of transcendental realms.

data.name: Generativemasks
data.description:
Generativemasks is a 10,000 unique NFT art created with Generative Art. This NFT automatically "generates" unique masks with different expressions one by one, and you can enjoy different colors of the masks every time you reload them on the NFT marketplaces.

The inspiration for this work came from discovering a sense of life in geometric patterns that are symmetrically arranged. With unexpected shapes and patterns, I tried to express the scary yet somehow charming atmosphere of Native American totem poles and indigenous Japanese Yokai.

contracts.name: Generativemasks
contracts.description:
Generativemasks is a 10,000 unique NFT art created with Generative Art. This NFT automatically "generates" unique masks with different expressions one by one, and you can enjoy different colors of the masks every time you reload them on the NFT marketplaces.

The inspiration for this work came from discovering a sense of life in geometric patterns that are symmetrically arranged. With unexpected shapes and patterns, I tried to express the scary yet somehow charming atmosphere of Native American totem poles and indigenous Japanese Yokai.

data.name: Generative Transfer Art Project 1
data.description:
⚠️Please read the description ⚠️

Generative Transfer Art Project 1 is the first in a series of experimental projects by [Wilson Cusack](https://twitter.com/WilsonCusack). Each NFT's image is created by its first 16 transfers, populating a 4x4 grid of squares. A new colored square is added on each transfer. The to address of the transfer determines the color.

There are 64 originals. Each original has up to 16 editions/copies, depending on the number of times transferred. Due to a bug, editions/copies mint more editions/copies when they are transferred. Please do due diligence to know whether you are buying an original or a copy. Copies do not add to the NFT art are when transferred, only the originals do. 

If the number at the end of the url matches the displayed "Token #...", then it is an original. There is also a [collection of wrapped originals](https://opensea.io/collection/wgtap1-og). Visit our website and Discord for more info.

data.name: Genesis Bitcoin
data.description:
The NFT memorabilia and proposed substitution of the unspendable BTC. Why? 

Own the greatest piece of crypto history. The Genesis Bitcoin NFT represents the ownership of the very first bitcoin mined by Satoshi Nakamoto himself on 3 January 2009.

The original genesis bitcoin can not be spent (transferred to someone) because the genesis block is hardcoded in the software - thus not a part of the blockchain database itself. This makes it invisible for processing while being counted in the total bitcoin supply.

Genesis Bitcoin NFT reclaims the value of the unspendable genesis bitcoin which is in unreachable territory in the manner of Terra nullius. So the genesis bitcoin can be spend vicariously through selling this Genesis Bitcoin NFT memorabilia. 

Each of the 50 interchangeable BTC from genesis block has its own representation as a single Genesis Bitcoin Non-Fungible Token. Therefore the full price of one Genesis Bitcoin NFT is 1 BTC.

Full story: Melouny.com#story

data.name: GENESIS FISH / FISH-TANK.IO
data.description:
The GENESIS FISH is a collection of 1111 unique Fish NFTs living on the ETH blockchain.

A motley crew of digital artists, game and blockchain developers came together to develop fish-tank.io. Their vision is to help offline artists to digitize their art, while also contributing to restoring our marine life. To foster this vision, the Gregory Hedrich Art Society’s artists created a unique set of 1’111 genesis fish NFTs with 170+ hand drawn traits, digitally mixed up to make each fish a unique piece of art with a random number of accessories and rarities. These accessories are reflected in its appearance and in its description. Although every combination is unique, 25% are rarer and 5% are legendary fish.

After minting your personal fish you can hold it in the member-tank in an exclusive section on our website,  or battle with other community members in the fish-race game.

https://fish-tank.io/ 💫 25% Donation to Save the Ocean Charitys

data.name: GENETICATS NFT
data.description:
GenomesDAO is a biotech DAO focused on the safe, private, and auditable monetization of genomic data. We’re merging the bleeding edge of encryption technology (AMD-SEV Vaults) with the blockchain to create the world’s first decentralized data brokering platform where users have full-custody and control of their genomic information.

Each Geneticat NFT includes a whole-genome sequencing kit and a genome mining vault (powered by AMD). Once we’ve sequenced and vaulted your genome — you receive a 1:1 generative NFT based on a set of queries from your genome.

data.description:
The Genuine Human Art Contract Collection currently features A YEAR AT THE BEACH - a series of unique time-dependent animated cyberpunk pixel art pieces. The scene you see depends on when you view it. 

On a summer day, a bright yellow lambo is parked up under the clear blue sky. On a winter night, a lone woman stands, wrapped up warm under the colourful stars. With eight different states, each animated pixel by pixel, A YEAR AT THE BEACH offers a new experience across the seasons. 

Contract: Artist owned ERC721 
Hosting files: Arweave Blockchain 

WEBSITE: https://ayearatthebeach.art/

data.name: Geohashes (Genesis Collection)
data.description:
A **geohash** encodes geographic location into a short string of letters and digits stored on chain.  Images and places are intentionally omitted for others to interpret and incorporate.

Geohashes Genesis contain 1,251 of the original 4 character geohashes and represent a block roughly 39.1km × 19.5km.  The contract mint is closed. These are all 1:1 and rarity depends on how you value location. 

They can be mapped to Earth or any coordinate system.  For instance **u09t** is a geohash that contains Paris, France.

data.name: GEOMETRICFORMS
data.description:
GEOMETRICFORMS is a collection of 100 unique FORMS NFTs - a digital version of generative geometry and post processed colour found in mathematics and art.

With only 100 NFTs created, the symmetry, geometry, lines, and colour of the artwork yield a subjective rarity. Stored as an ERC-721 token on the Ethereum blockchain for immutable history and decentralized ownership.

Purchasing a GEOMETRICFORMS will cost 0.5 ETH each

Owning FORMS will grant you access to monthly art raffles airdropping from Geometric Curated Collections, and minters who hold until 2022 are eligible to claim a high quality physically framed art print out mailed for free.
